videos.headline: Fight between South Carolina, LSU leads to several ejections
videos.description: Kamilla Cardoso shoves Flau'jae Johnson to the floor, leading to the LSU and South Carolina benches clearing and a lot of ejections for both teams.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Fight between South Carolina, LSU leads to several ejections) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gamecocks earn eighth SEC title with thrilling win vs. LSU
videos.description: MiLaysia Fulwiley scores a career-high 24 points to lead top-seeded South Carolina past the 2-seed Tigers' four double-digit scorers in the 79-72 championship win.

videos.headline: South Carolina celebrates SEC title win over LSU
videos.description: South Carolina finishes off a victory over LSU to win the SEC title and remain undefeated on the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (South Carolina celebrates SEC title win over LSU) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dawn Staley apologizes for South Carolina-LSU scuffle
videos.description: South Carolina coach Dawn Staley apologizes for the scuffle that broke out with LSU near the end of the SEC title game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Interview (Dawn Staley apologizes for South Carolina-LSU scuffle) 2024/03/10

videos.headline: Staley credits players for Gamecocks' latest SEC title
videos.description: Dawn Staley credits her South Carolina players for defeating LSU, 79-70, for the SEC Women's Tournament crown, the eighth in the last 10 years for the coach and her program.

videos.headline: Hometown hero Fulwiley handles business in champ win
videos.description: South Carolina freshman MiLaysia Fulwiley says she had to stay composed and poised after she drops game-high 24 points in the 79-72 SEC championship win over LSU.

videos.headline: Staley says 'sense of belief' fuels Gamecocks' title runs
videos.description: Dawn Staley reiterates that South Carolina's latest SEC Tournament championship is the result of hard work and her players' unwavering belief in being the best.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Interview (Staley SC on set NEW) 240310

videos.headline: South Carolina's Fulwiley reveals plan for tourney success
videos.description: Freshman MiLaysia Fulwiley says the plan for her and the Gamecocks in the SEC Tournament was simply this: 'Stay cool, stay calm, take care of business.'

videos.headline: Mulkey: I wish Kamilla Cardoso would've pushed Angel Reese
videos.description: LSU coach Kim Mulkey explains why she wishes South Carolina's Kamilla Cardoso would have pushed Angel Reese instead of Flau'jae Johnson.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Presser (Mulkey: I wish Kamilla Cardoso would've pushed Angel Reese) 2024/3/10
